Description: Fix 64-bit portability issues
 - staraz_init() returned long* but pal[] is int[]; on LP64 long is 8 bytes
   causing a pointer type mismatch and potential memory corruption
 - Use Uint32* instead of int* for SDL pixel buffer (SDL_MapRGB returns Uint32)
